#4900
Academy Entrance~
@@NYou stand in the grand entrance hall of the @@WAcademy of Adventure@@N.

Tall stone pillars rise to a vaulted ceiling above.  Torchlight flickers

across carved murals depicting heroes in battle, explorers navigating

dungeons, and merchants haggling over goods.  A large sign hangs on the

wall, welcoming new adventurers.

The path continues @@ynorth@@N deeper into the academy.

~
