sign~
@@WLesson I: Movement@@N


You move around the world by typing directions:


  @@yNORTH@@N (or just @@yN@@N)    @@ySOUTH@@N (or just @@yS@@N)

  @@yEAST@@N  (or just @@yE@@N)    @@yWEST@@N  (or just @@yW@@N)

  @@yUP@@N    (or just @@yU@@N)    @@yDOWN@@N  (or just @@yD@@N)


To see the obvious exits in your current room, type '@@yEXITS@@N'.


To look around and read the room description again, type '@@yLOOK@@N'.


Go @@yEAST@@N now to practice moving in all six directions.

When you are done practicing, come back here and go @@yNORTH@@N.


~
S
