sign~
@@WLesson II: Doors and Locks@@N


Sometimes exits are blocked by doors.  You can interact with doors using:


  @@yOPEN <direction>@@N   -- Open a closed door (e.g. '@@yOPEN DOWN@@N')

  @@yCLOSE <direction>@@N  -- Close an open door

  @@yUNLOCK <direction>@@N -- Unlock a locked door (you need the right key!)

  @@yLOCK <direction>@@N   -- Lock a door with a key


The door leading @@yDOWN@@N is closed.  Type '@@yOPEN DOWN@@N' to open it,

then go @@yDOWN@@N.


~
