sign~
@@WLesson V: Items and Equipment (Part 1)@@N


You can interact with items on the ground and in your inventory:


  @@yGET <item>@@N       -- Pick up an item from the ground

  @@yDROP <item>@@N      -- Drop an item from your inventory

  @@yINVENTORY@@N (or @@yI@@N) -- See what you are carrying

  @@yHOLD <item>@@N      -- Hold an item (like a light source)

  @@yPUT <item> <container>@@N -- Put an item into a bag or chest

  @@yGET <item> <container>@@N -- Take an item out of a container


Try it now!  Pick up the @@ybag@@N and @@ylantern@@N on the floor:


  Type '@@yGET BAG@@N' then '@@yGET LANTERN@@N' then '@@yHOLD LANTERN@@N'.

  You can also type '@@yGET ALL@@N' to pick up everything at once.


When ready, go @@yWEST@@N.


~
S
