sign~
@@WLesson VII: Score, Worth, and Leveling@@N


Keep track of your character's progress with these commands:


  @@ySCORE@@N   -- See your stats, level, HP, mana, and more

  @@yWORTH@@N   -- See your gold, experience earned, and experience needed to level


@@WLeveling Up:@@N

  When you earn enough experience, type '@@yGAIN@@N' to advance a level.

  @@RIMPORTANT:@@N You must be near a @@Wtrainer@@N to use GAIN!

  There is a trainer at the recall point.  Type '@@yRECALL@@N' to go there,

  then type '@@yGAIN@@N' near the trainer to level up.

  You can gain levels in multiple classes!  This is called @@Wmulti-classing@@N.


@@WTraining and Practicing:@@N

  @@yTRAIN@@N     -- Spend training sessions to raise attributes (STR, INT, etc.)

  @@yLEARN@@N     -- See your learned spells and skills


Try '@@ySCORE@@N' and '@@yWORTH@@N' now to see your current stats.


When ready, go @@yEAST@@N.


~
S
