sign~
@@W*** Congratulations, Graduate! ***@@N


You have completed the Academy of Adventure!


Kill the sage to claim your @@Wdiploma@@N -- it has magical properties!


@@WYour Next Steps:@@N

  1. Type '@@yRECALL@@N' to teleport to the temple.

  2. There is a @@Wtrainer mob@@N at recall -- type '@@yGAIN@@N' to advance your level!

  3. Then go @@yUP@@N, @@yUP@@N to begin exploring the next area!


@@WUseful Commands to Remember:@@N

  @@yRECALL@@N  -- Teleport back to the temple at any time

  @@ySAVE@@N    -- Save your character (auto-saves every few minutes)

  @@yHELP@@N    -- Get help on any topic

  @@yWHO@@N     -- See who else is playing

  @@yQUIT@@N    -- Leave the game (your character is saved)


May your adventures be legendary!


~
S
